    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Discretization error is quantified and within acceptance criteria. Output comparison confirms model predictions agree with experimental data within 20% across all operating points. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD hemolysis model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
